cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.CY 

This paper deals with automated assessment, which involves natural language processing and machine learning. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also uses neural networks for multi-task learning, which falls under the sub-categories of cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also involves information retrieval techniques for feature extraction, which falls under the sub-category of cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Finally, the paper deals with the application of automated assessment in education, which falls under the sub-category of cs.CY (Computers and Society).
